it's a public place.

165
00:17:02,080 --> 00:17:06,748
Fleshies ain't supposed to have this.
Where'd you get it?

166
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:13,940
The Spooker lmage Catalog. So how come
you guys decided to move here?

167
00:17:14,047 --> 00:17:18,865
