Though it is a nice location.

168
00:17:18,943 --> 00:17:22,389
Oh, yes. Excellent view too.
Something of a fixer-upper though.

169
00:17:22,496 --> 00:17:25,560
Will you two shut your yaps?

170
00:17:26,625 --> 00:17:29,689
