175
00:17:43,745 --> 00:17:46,710
Don't eat beans around the campfire.

176
00:17:49,634 --> 00:17:51,289
Come on, guys.

177
00:17:53,727 --> 00:17:57,750
Beat it, biped. You don't scare right.

178
00:17:58,689 --> 00:18:00,792
