179
00:18:01,536 --> 00:18:03,901
Oh, my gosh, I'm late for school.

180
00:18:38,914 --> 00:18:40,919
Here they come!

181
00:18:56,416 --> 00:18:59,708
All right, everybody. Settle down, folks.

182
